headline: Tequila is the Fastest Growing Spirit: Lisa Barlow
summary: Lisa Barlow, founder of Vida Tequila, says expansion is always the goal, noting the brand also offers a hard seltzer in Ulta. She tells Romaine Bostick and Katie Greifeld on "The Close" that tequila is the fastest-growing spirit category.
